{"tid":1043150,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"關愛座hunter有冇考慮叫理大生集體退學？","createTime":"2019-03-02T05:05:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-06T10:41:29.000Z","uid":38523,"like":30,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"a92626294dafb53366d3c95f1ffa41a9300bdf0a","tid":1043150,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T05:05:11.000Z","msg":"你係個比人控制既制度入面<br />\n可以為自己爭取乜野？<br />\n叫學校施捨公義比你？<br />\n所以當個制度已經廢左<br />\n就應該跳出來抗爭啦<br />\n依加係最好時機啦<br />\n唔做係咪即係撐理大？<br />\n定大家覺得理大個制度有險可守？<br />\n如果係點解跟校方個機制上訴<br />\n如果唔係點解要唔叫理大集團退學？<br />\n我勸關愛座hunter應該發起理大學生退學<br />\n雖然你屈話我 但我都可以提番你提出過既一個策略<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/02/130103_7e0b3d3708459a182d6a17ba072c71b2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F02%2F130103_7e0b3d3708459a182d6a17ba072c71b2.png&h=8f204974&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e1d1b7976c5d602c3f90fa5ec9090249245b51a6","tid":1043150,"uid":38523,"like":13,"dislike":6,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T05:07:49.000Z","msg":"理性討論點幫關愛座hunter<br />\n成日話應該一單還一單<br />\n我依加提出其中一個佢本人提出過既方法<br />\n大家點睇"},{"pid":"e0adfec836e0ed276ce7aafef343489983ebf29e","tid":1043150,"uid":38523,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T05:10:09.000Z","msg":"請問理大學係咪為理大好？"},{"pid":"472eb420c06e165adcb9edd446b1a9e786e22864","tid":1043150,"uid":24140,"like":7,"dislike":6,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T05:11:09.000Z","msg":"同五毛話：要反共產黨點解唔離開香港<br />\n有咩分別？"},{"pid":"89489237f4469284d3087fc1a2a75540ede1c5b7","tid":1043150,"uid":132038,"like":12,"dislike":3,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T05:11:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7b9c2548cecfe51196a69e666a989d668d76678f","tid":1043150,"uid":38523,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"quote":{"pid":"472eb420c06e165adcb9edd446b1a9e786e22864","tid":1043150,"uid":24140,"like":7,"dislike":6,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T05:11:09.000Z","msg":"